2014-03-17 15:31:57	jkelly	What are the pros/cons of SSH compared to FTP?
2014-03-17 15:32:33	@smrtz|nix	they're two diffrent protocals.  that's like asking the pros/cons of http vs imap.
2014-03-17 15:32:58	@smrtz|nix	ssh lets you create a secure tunnel to an endpoint, what you do through that tunnel is up to you.
2014-03-17 15:33:14	@smrtz|nix	If I were you, I'd use sftp, it's ftp through an ssh tunnel.
2014-03-17 15:33:34	@smrtz|nix	or scp.  either one will work.
